		<title>This Week on Bear radio: The conservation of risk and the illusory safety of hedging</title>
		<link>http://msurkan.podbean.com/2011/02/23/this-week-on-bear-radio-the-conservation-of-risk-and-the-illusory-safety-of-hedging/</link>
